The paper focuses on using QR Codes for storing and transmitting encrypted messages securely. This falls under the category of cryptography (cs.CR). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of QR Codes in various sectors such as business, government, and communication networks, which could also fall under the categories of cybersecurity (cs.CY), information theory (cs.IT), software engineering (cs.SE), and multimedia (cs.MM).
